channel.title: Tehpk-scape is back, and now a 639!
channel.description:
TEHPK-SCAPE IS BACK!
639 ECONOMY BASED
___________________________________________________________________________
Dungeoneering Caves
Crystal Mines Frost Dragons
Quick Prayers Teleblock
All shops
Theiving stalls at home
Working Slayer Rewards
Pk points (Exchange for pk tokens with Nastroth)
Mobilising Armies Titles (Depending on how many people you killed)
Slayer helm assembling, and disassembling
Ring of slaying
Dragontooth island holding:Chaos Dwarves
Guthix Mages
Elite Black Knights
Slayer points working like RuneScape but different point amounts
Fish-able Rocktail and Cavefish
NPCs dropping shards and charms
Ancient mace special attack (Couldn't find gfx or anim)
Storm of Armadyl
Kal'ger the Warmonger
Kolodion (somewhat customized)
Necromancers
Slayer helm giving greater attack percentage on tasks
More, but I don't remember it all.
Sagittarian bolts and arrows (with special)
____________________________________________________________________ CUSTOM CLIENT, AUTO CONNECTS!
- http://uppit.com/e4fdpdjhtr06/tehpk-scape_client.zip
____________________________________________________________________ Owner & Coder: Tehpk
____________________________________________________________________
I HAVE RULES, IF YOU DO NOT RESPECT MY RULES, THEN DON’T PLAY!
::RULES
